+Subject: [PATCH 5/5] test(integration): cover AI commit message generation
+
+---
+ .../tests/commit/generate_commit_message.go   | 42 +++++++++++++++++++
+ ...erate_commit_message_malformed_response.go | 37 ++++++++++++++++
+ pkg/integration/tests/test_list.go            |  2 +
